Package: diceRoller
Title: Simulated dice roller
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Brooks", "Perkins-Jechow", , "bperkinsj@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Simulates rolling a die or dice with a specified number of 
  faces. Can provide either the result of one die roll, the result of 
  adding several dice together, or the mean, maximum, and minimum (in that order)
  of several dice.
